<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="chr.wilck;;140" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">WChr140</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Πα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied>εχώτης ὁ καὶ Πανάρης τῶν κεκοσμητευκότων τῆς Ὀξυρυγχειτῶν 

    <lb n="2"/>πόλεως διὰ Γεμέλλου φίλου Ἀπολλωνίῳ <choice><corr>σημειογράφῳ</corr><sic>σημιογραφω</sic></choice> χαίρειν. συνέστησά σοι 

    <lb n="3"/>Χαιράμμωνα δοῦλον πρὸς μάθησιν σημείων ὧν ἐπίσταται ὁ υἱός <subst><add place="inline">σου</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">μου</del></subst> 

    <lb n="4"/>Δι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>νύσιος ἐπὶ χρόνον ἔτη δύο <num value="2"/> ἀπὸ τοῦ ἐνεστῶτος μηνὸς Φαμενὼθ τοῦ 

    <lb n="5"/>ὀκτωκαιδεκάτου ἔτους Ἀντωνίνου Καίσαρος τοῦ κυρίου μισθοῦ τοῦ συμπεφω-

    <lb n="6"/>νημένου πρὸς ἀλλήλους ἀργυρίου δραχμῶν ἑκατὸν εἴκοσι <num value="120"/> χωρὶς ἑορτι-

    <lb n="7"/>κῶν, ἐξ ὧν ἔσχες τὴν πρώτην δόσιν ἐν <subst><add place="inline">δραχμαῖς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">δραγμαις</del></subst> τεσσαράκοντα <num value="40"/>, τὴν δὲ 

    <lb n="8"/>δευτέραν <choice><corr>λήψει</corr><sic>ληψη</sic></choice> τοῦ παιδὸς ἀνειληφότος τὸ κο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>εντάρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>ον ὅλον ἐν δρα-

    <lb n="9"/>χ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied>αῖς τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εσσ</supplied>αράκοντα <num value="40"/>, τὴν δὲ τρίτην λήψομαι ἐπὶ τέλει τοῦ χρόνου τοῦ 

    <lb n="10"/>παιδὸς ἐκ παντὸς λόγου πεζοῦ γράφοντος καὶ <choice><corr>ἀναγιγνώσκοντος</corr><sic>αναγεινωσ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κον</supplied>τος</sic></choice> ἀμέμπτως 

    <lb n="11"/>τὰς <sic>δὲ</sic> λοιπὰς δραχμὰς τεσσαράκοντα <num value="40"/>. ἐὰν δὲ ἐντὸς τοῦ χ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied>όνου αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="12"/>ἀπαρτίσῃς οὐκ <subst><add place="inline">ἐκδέξομαι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">εκδεχομαι</del></subst> τὴν προκειμένην προθεσμ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ί</supplied>αν, οὐκ ἐξόντος 

    <lb n="13"/>μοι ἐντὸς τοῦ χρόνου τὸν παῖδα ἀποσπᾶν, παραμενεῖ δέ σ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ι μετὰ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὸ</supplied>ν χρό<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νον ὅσας</supplied> 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐὰν ἀργήσῃ ἡμέρας ἢ μῆνας. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="18">ιη</num> Αὐτοκράτορος Καίσαρος Τίτου Αἰλίου Ἁδριανοῦ 

    <lb n="15"/><choice><corr>Ἀντωνίνου</corr><sic>αντωνεινου</sic></choice> Σεβαστοῦ Εὐσεβοῦς Φαμενὼθ <num value="5">ε</num>. </ab></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="155" notBefore="155" type="textDate" value="0155-03-01">1. März 155</date></p></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Vgl. Comunicazioni 5, 2003, S. 20-23.</p></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">724</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">20424</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">724</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;4;724" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">181</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">145</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.20424" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere